<th class="fn summary" colspan="2" style="background: lightsteelblue; text-align: center; vertical-align: middle;">Carl Philipp Gottlieb von Clausewitz</th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan="2" style="background: lightsteelblue; text-align: center; vertical-align: middle;">July 1, 1780–November 16, 1831</td>
</tr>
