<td colspan="2" style="text-align: center; font-size: 90%; border-bottom: 1px solid #aaa; line-height: 1.5em;"><a href="/wiki/File:Clausewitz.jpg" class="image" title="Image:Clausewitz.jpg"><img alt="Image:Clausewitz.jpg" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/a/a0/Clausewitz.jpg" width="225" height="300" border="0" /></a><br />
